  OrderIdx: 4
  Title: "D\u1EA4U \u1EA4N & T\u1EF0 H\xC0O"
  HexCode: 0x3B
  Content:
  - "Sinh vi\xEAn UIT kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 ghi d\u1EA5u trong n\u01B0\u1EDBc m\xE0 c\xF2n
    nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EA1i di\u1EC7n Vi\u1EC7t Nam tham gia c\xE1c \u0111\u1EA5u
    tr\u01B0\u1EDDng h\u1ECDc thu\u1EADt ________ nh\u01B0 ACM-ICPC, Olympic Tin
    h\u1ECDc ch\xE2u \xC1 v\xE0 nhi\u1EC1u cu\u1ED9c thi b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt tr\xEAn
    th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi."
  - "Kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 ghi d\u1EA5u t\u1EA1i c\xE1c \u0111\u1EA5u tr\u01B0\u1EDDng
    h\u1ECDc thu\u1EADt v\xE0 c\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7 qu\u1ED1c t\u1EBF, sinh vi\xEAn UIT
    c\xF2n li\xEAn t\u1EE5c \u0111\xF3ng g\xF3p nhi\u1EC1u c\xF4ng tr\xECnh nghi\xEAn
    c\u1EE9u v\xE0 b\xE0i b\xE1o khoa h\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\xF4ng nh\u1EADn
    trong v\xE0 ngo\xE0i n\u01B0\u1EDBc. \\n Nh\u1EEFng gi\u1EA3i th\u01B0\u1EDFng,
    th\xE0nh t\xEDch v\xE0 \u0111\xF3ng g\xF3p \u1EA5y \u0111\xE3 tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh
    m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n quan tr\u1ECDng t\u1EA1o n\xEAn nh\u1EEFng ________ \u0111\xE1ng
    t\u1EF1 h\xE0o c\u1EE7a UIT su\u1ED1t 20 n\u0103m qua."
  Keys:
  - key: 5
    value: 'QUOCTE '
  - key: 9
    value: 'THANHTUU '
